SENATE AND ASSEMBLY, DO ENACT AS FOLLOWS:
1 Section 1. NRS 232.162 is hereby amended to read as follows:
2 232.162 1. The Sagebrush Ecosystem Council is hereby created in the
3 Department. The Council consists of:
4 (a) The following nine voting members appointed by the Governor:

